oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: UNICEF tour - Australia - 1972 - part 4
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Part four of a 1972 UNICEF fundraiser tour performance in Australia. Featuring Tex Ritter (host), Buddy Williams (performer), and Ray Sanders (performer).
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Tex Ritter; Buddy Williams; Ray Sanders
